  "prompt": "Can I put a sleep number matress on a platform frame?",
  "response": "Yes, you can put a Sleep Number mattress on a platform bed frame. Sleep Number mattresses are designed to be compatible with most bed frames, including platform beds. Just ensure that the platform bed frame has a solid, flat surface or slats that are no more than 2.5 inches apart to provide adequate support for the mattress. Additionally, make sure the frame is sturdy enough to support the weight of the mattress and the sleepers.",
